1
00:00:08,209 --> 00:00:10,085
(Chris Tucci) Muraho ikaze nanone.

2
00:00:10,086 --> 00:00:13,875
Iki ni igice cya 4.7
cy'incamake y'icyumweru.

3
00:00:13,876 --> 00:00:18,043
Mucuti wanjye Marc Gruber
agiye hanze mu minota ishize.

4
00:00:18,066 --> 00:00:22,025
Ndakeka ari kuri tweeter
asubiza bamwe muri mwe

5
00:00:22,026 --> 00:00:23,889
mu bufashe bwo kuri interineti butangwa nyuma y'isomo

6
00:00:23,890 --> 00:00:27,464
anasubiza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga
ibibazo bimwe byanyu,

7
00:00:27,465 --> 00:00:32,237
ndanakeka ko yansize hano
kugirango mpangane n'abarebyi

8
00:00:32,238 --> 00:00:35,098
ku burebure bukabije bw'icyumweru cya kane.

9
00:00:36,608 --> 00:00:39,616
Ndabihanganisha ku burebure
icyumweru cya kane cyagize.

10
00:00:39,617 --> 00:00:41,921
Sinigeze menya uburebure
kizagira.

11
00:00:41,922 --> 00:00:45,954
Hari binshi byo kurebaho
mu buryo bwo gushora imari,

12
00:00:45,955 --> 00:00:50,293
niyo mpamvu byarangiye
bitinze ho gato.

13
00:00:50,294 --> 00:00:53,579
Noneho nashakaga kwisegura
kuri buri umwe muri mwe

14
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:55,550
kubw'uburebure bw'icyumweru cya kane.

15
00:00:55,551 --> 00:01:00,124
Noneho turakora akazi kihuse
kuri izi nshakake

16
00:01:00,125 --> 00:01:02,399
twiyibutsa
icyo twabonye muri iki cyumweru.

17
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:06,879
Ikintu cya mbere twavuzeho 
cyari amafaranga uba ukeneye,

18
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:10,894
kandi nk'uko mubyibuka, twakoze
imibare myinshi

19
00:01:10,895 --> 00:01:13,526
yirekana muri make,

20
00:01:13,527 --> 00:01:16,589
amafaranga yose
umuntu yakenera kugira;

21
00:01:16,590 --> 00:01:20,419
wongeyeho ko twanavuze
ibyo umwaka ku mwaka,

22
00:01:20,420 --> 00:01:23,062
amafaranga 
wakenera buri mwaka

23
00:01:23,063 --> 00:01:26,582
ugendeye ku giciro cyawe bwite
ndetse n'inyungu uteganya,

24
00:01:26,583 --> 00:01:30,024
aribyo ufite gukora,
kandi ugahora ubikurikirana buri gihe.

25
00:01:30,854 --> 00:01:33,964
Noneho kuri iki gishushanyo,
nkuko mubibona, iki ni kimwe,

26
00:01:33,965 --> 00:01:36,319
mushobora kuba mwarahaze iki gishushanyo,

27
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:41,469
cyerekana amafaranga
umuntu yateganya gukenera,

28
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:45,254
Kandi aho amafaranga yinjira n'ayasohoka yiyongera,
Kandi aho binganira,

29
00:01:45,255 --> 00:01:47,500
n'igishoro cy'ibanze.

30
00:01:47,501 --> 00:01:50,751
Twanavuze ku nzego
zo gukurikirana umushinga

31
00:01:50,752 --> 00:01:53,530
bijyanye n'
ibihe bitandukanye,

32
00:01:53,531 --> 00:01:55,710
uzagira mu gukurikirana.

33
00:01:55,711 --> 00:02:01,515
Kandi ududomo two ku ruhande rw'imoso z'iki gishushanyo
tuyita imbuto cyangwa ikigero gitangira,

34
00:02:01,516 --> 00:02:03,518
kandi utudomo two ku ruhande rw'iburyo,

35
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:07,790
uko igihe kigenda cyangwa ugatangira kugurisha
ibintu nibwo ugira igicuruzwa nyacyo

36
00:02:07,791 --> 00:02:12,837
noneho uziringira kongera
ukwagura kumwe cyangwa wagure mu butunzi.

37
00:02:13,197 --> 00:02:15,822
Noneho twasiye n'abashatse itandukaniro
hagati yibyo bintu.

38
00:02:15,823 --> 00:02:19,863
Twarakomeje tuganira
ku bwoko butandukanye bwo kongera umutungo.

39
00:02:19,864 --> 00:02:23,902
Nk'urugero, impano,
ubufasha, kugiriza umwenda,

40
00:02:24,602 --> 00:02:28,086
gutanga inguzanyo, cyangwa gutanga
imigabane y'ibice bya business yawe,

41
00:02:28,776 --> 00:02:31,265
ukwiharira ndetse no gucunga
igice cya bisinesi yawe,

42
00:02:31,472 --> 00:02:34,471
kandi twanavuze ho gato
ku ideni rihinduka.

43
00:02:34,472 --> 00:02:38,154
Noneho, twarebye urutonde

44
00:02:38,155 --> 00:02:42,516
rw'ubwoko rw'abashoramari batandukanye
ushobora guhura nabyo,

45
00:02:42,517 --> 00:02:47,283
kandi twarebyemo bike
mu byiza n'ibibi cya buri cyose.

46
00:02:47,284 --> 00:02:49,999
Kandi nkuko mubyibuka kuri buri kimwe muri ibi,

47
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:54,126
twanaciye mu rutonde
rwa ibiciro biteganwa

48
00:02:55,276 --> 00:02:58,076
n'amafaranga
wateganya kwakira.

49
00:02:58,636 --> 00:03:02,021
Twanibukiranije
ko iki cyari kiza

50
00:03:02,022 --> 00:03:05,430
ku biryanye, nk'uko mubizi
n'ubukungu bw'inganda

51
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,743
aho ubukungu bw'igihugu mu mwaka ari 50,000,

52
00:03:11,744 --> 00:03:14,743
bityo izo zisaba kuzivugurura

53
00:03:14,744 --> 00:03:19,000
bitewe nawe
ugendeye ku musaruro wa buri muturage mu gihugu.

54
00:03:19,550 --> 00:03:21,816
Ariko muri buri buryo, ibyo dufite

55
00:03:21,817 --> 00:03:26,229
ni urutonde rw'inkomoko,
amafaranga kuri buri nkomoko,

56
00:03:26,230 --> 00:03:30,263
noneho nanarebye itandukaniro
riri hagati ya bike cyangwa byinshi, ku ruhande rw'imoso,

57
00:03:30,264 --> 00:03:33,298
aricyo imbuto nyayo
na igishoro cyo gutangira,

58
00:03:33,299 --> 00:03:36,400
no ku ruhande rw'iburyo,
mu iguni ry'iburyo ryo hasi,

59
00:03:36,401 --> 00:03:39,531
ari byo bigenga kwaguka no gukura.

60
00:03:41,271 --> 00:03:42,862
Noneho kuru buri nkomoko,

61
00:03:42,863 --> 00:03:46,592
twarebye bimwe mu byiza
n'ibibi bya buri yose

62
00:03:46,593 --> 00:03:48,991
tugendeye ku bintu bitatu ngenderwaho.

63
00:03:48,992 --> 00:03:52,941
Icyambere cyabaye igishoro:
Ni amafaranga angahe wabona?

64
00:03:52,942 --> 00:03:55,789
Ni ukuhe kuboneka,
igihe byamara,igiciro n'ibindi ?

65
00:03:55,790 --> 00:03:59,125
ibigenderwaho mu micungire,
ari nayo nkunga bashobora kuguha

66
00:03:59,126 --> 00:04:03,110
mu gikorwa cyo gutangira, mu icungamutungo,
cyangwa imenyekanisha gaciro bashobora kwongera;

67
00:04:03,111 --> 00:04:04,450
cyangwa ibindi bigenderwaho,

68
00:04:04,451 --> 00:04:09,730
aribyo buryo inkomoko zigenga
kuva kuri wowe cyangwa ikipe mwatangiranye.

69
00:04:09,731 --> 00:04:11,750
Ndakeka numvise Marc aje none aha.

70
00:04:11,751 --> 00:04:13,680
Ndakeka agiye agiye kumfasha
kuri ino ngingo ikurikira,

71
00:04:13,681 --> 00:04:15,569
kandi tugiye gusoza

72
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:17,447
ibyari bisigaye ku mwine z'iki cyumweru.

73
00:04:18,437 --> 00:04:20,985
Noneho, ibyo twakoze
kuri kino, niba twibuka,

74
00:04:20,986 --> 00:04:25,247
nuko twashyize ibintu bigenderwaho
mu byiciro by'amasoko y'ibishoro.

75
00:04:25,248 --> 00:04:27,515
(Marc Gruber) Izi
ni icyamake z'abanze

76
00:04:27,516 --> 00:04:31,059
kuko ikubwira ku bijyanye n'igihe,
n'amafaranga wateganya kubona, n'ibindi.

77
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:34,439
Ntudushaka kwinjira cyane
muri buri gice kuko twabivuzeho.

78
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,628
Twarabisoje. (baraseka)

79
00:04:35,629 --> 00:04:36,948
Iyi ni incamake,

80
00:04:36,949 --> 00:04:40,511
ariko, ndakeka ko ari iby'ingenzi
kufata bino mu mutwe, noneho wanabifotoza,

81
00:04:40,512 --> 00:04:44,033
noneho ubukoreshe nk'igikoresho cyo kwifashisha
mu gihe kizaza, kandi twari dufite ikindi gice--

82
00:04:44,034 --> 00:04:46,489
Ibintu bimwe no kwagura igishoro.

83
00:04:46,490 --> 00:04:49,039
Noneho icyo dufite hano mu ncamake

84
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:53,317
nuko wakwagura igishoro biragaragaza
uburyo butandukanye wagenderaho ufata umwanzuro.

85
00:04:54,287 --> 00:04:58,519
Bumwe mu buryo bwo kwagura igishoro
bwiza ku bashoramari

86
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:01,043
ni ugukoresha interineti
kuko bukoresha web,

87
00:05:01,044 --> 00:05:04,486
aho wabona abantu benshi
mpuzamahanga bo guteza imbere umushinga wawe.

88
00:05:04,487 --> 00:05:05,487
Sibyo.

89
00:05:05,488 --> 00:05:07,506
Noneho ibyo twavuzeho iki cyumweru byari

90
00:05:07,507 --> 00:05:10,720
uburyo butandukanye bwo gushora imari
hakoreshejwe gukoresha interineti.

91
00:05:10,721 --> 00:05:14,873
Noneho nkuko twabibonye, byaba
isoko nziza yo gushora imari.

92
00:05:14,874 --> 00:05:18,458
Mvugiye muri rusange,abaterankunga
ntibabona amafaranga,

93
00:05:18,459 --> 00:05:21,488
nubwo twabiganiriyeho
mu gice ubwacyo

94
00:05:21,489 --> 00:05:23,203
igihe babona amafaranga,

95
00:05:23,204 --> 00:05:26,745
n'uko ibihugu bitandukanye bihindura amategeko
ku bijyanye no gushora amafaranga.

96
00:05:29,935 --> 00:05:33,709
Ushobora gukoresha iyi nkunga mu gutangiza
umushinga wawe ugendeye kuri gahunda yawe.

97
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:37,372
Ariko utegekwa nanone gukora ibyo,
kuko uba uri kubona amafaranga.

98
00:05:37,373 --> 00:05:41,298
Abantu bateganya ikintu cyawe,
kandi ukwiye kubikurikirana

99
00:05:41,299 --> 00:05:44,012
Naho ubundi hazabamo
ibibazo by'amategeko

100
00:05:44,013 --> 00:05:45,832
iyo utishyuye amasezerano.

101
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:47,682
Kandi nanone ni na bibi
ku gaciro kawe

102
00:05:47,683 --> 00:05:48,998
iyo utishyuye amasezerano.

103
00:05:48,999 --> 00:05:50,668
-Ibyo ni byo.
-Uko niko kuri.

104
00:05:50,669 --> 00:05:53,608
Twanavuze ku
moko y'ibishoro,

105
00:05:53,609 --> 00:05:56,414
noneho aha dushobora gutandukanya
hagati y'ibitarangira

106
00:05:56,417 --> 00:05:59,241
aho ukora gahunda
yo kugira umubare runaka w' amafaranga,

107
00:05:59,242 --> 00:06:02,133
Kandi uba ufite kwongera byibura X
cyangwa ntubone ikintu na kimwe,

108
00:06:02,134 --> 00:06:05,464
cyangwa ibishoro bihinduka aho wabasha
kubika ayariyo yose wabonye

109
00:06:05,465 --> 00:06:08,002
kugeza aho ushakiye kuhagararira,

110
00:06:08,003 --> 00:06:10,142
ndetse n'ibyiza
n'ibibi byayo.

111
00:06:10,143 --> 00:06:13,666
Noneho icyanyuma twaganiriyeho
muri iki cyumweru ni ikigero cyisumbuye.

112
00:06:13,667 --> 00:06:17,159
ni icunga mafaranga
kuko nkuko twabivuze,

113
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:21,125
amafaranga mu mushinga wawe ni nk'umwuka
uhumeka, nk'ikiremwa muntu,

114
00:06:21,126 --> 00:06:24,227
kandi iyo udafite umwuka
uhumeka, ubura umwuka.

115
00:06:24,228 --> 00:06:27,500
Ninako iyo udafite amafaranga
mu mushinga, ujya mu bihombo.

116
00:06:27,501 --> 00:06:30,397
Noneho muri make, gucunga
amafaranga yawe ni iby'ingezi cyane,

117
00:06:30,398 --> 00:06:33,166
noneho hari hari ingingo eshatu
z'umwihariko werekanye.

118
00:06:33,167 --> 00:06:36,692
Izo ni igihe cyo gusohora amafaranga.
Uko bagishaka.

119
00:06:36,693 --> 00:06:39,071
Twarabirebye
kandi byaduhaye igitekerezo

120
00:06:39,083 --> 00:06:41,917
cy'igihe
wakomeza amategeko.

121
00:06:42,667 --> 00:06:45,576
Binafasha gukora gahunda yo gukusanya amafaranga

122
00:06:45,577 --> 00:06:48,062
kuko ukeneye kumenya
igihe ukenye kwongera amafaranga,

123
00:06:48,063 --> 00:06:50,948
kandi ukenye kumenya amabwiriza
ugiye kwongereraho amafaranga.

124
00:06:50,949 --> 00:06:53,308
Noneho bwa nyuma, ikigero cyawe cyo hejuru
kigaragaza

125
00:06:53,309 --> 00:06:55,463
intege nke ziboneka
mu kwinjiza amafaranga

126
00:06:55,464 --> 00:06:59,292
mu kugaragaza ko ukeneye
guhorana ibyinjira niba bishoboka

127
00:06:59,293 --> 00:07:01,639
kurenza kuba waba udafite ibyinjira.

128
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,147
Noneho mu buryo, bituma utekereza

129
00:07:03,148 --> 00:07:04,867
kubyo wateguye
nk'uburyo bw'ibyinjira,

130
00:07:04,868 --> 00:07:06,815
kandi ko hoshobora kubaho
uburyo bwiza.

131
00:07:06,816 --> 00:07:09,640
Kandi bigarutse mu biganiro
ku bijyanye n'imitekerereze yo kwiyemeza umurimo

132
00:07:09,641 --> 00:07:10,818
twamaze kugira

133
00:07:10,819 --> 00:07:13,678
kuko abashoramari beza
baba bazi kureba umushinga

134
00:07:13,679 --> 00:07:14,978
mu mwande nyinshi,

135
00:07:14,979 --> 00:07:17,762
bakumvikana, bagerageza
kumva impande zitandukanye

136
00:07:17,763 --> 00:07:20,611
zo, muri icyo gihe,
kubaka uburyo bw'ibyinjiye

137
00:07:20,612 --> 00:07:23,454
bishobora kuba byaruta ibyo
urimo utekereza.

138
00:07:23,455 --> 00:07:27,474
Tuzabivugaho cyane
mu cyumweru gitaha mu gice cya gatanu nabyo.

139
00:07:27,475 --> 00:07:30,089
Noneho ibi bituganishije ku musozo
w'icyumweru cya kane.

140
00:07:30,090 --> 00:07:32,389
Ndabizi ko ukwezi kwashije.
Igihe kirihuta.

141
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:34,488
Igihe kirihuta, turi kwishimana.

142
00:07:34,489 --> 00:07:39,252
Ariko iki ni bine bya gatanu;80%
bya MOOC twarangije, haracyabura icyumweru kimwe.

143
00:07:39,253 --> 00:07:41,843
Kizaba ari icyumweru
mu gufata agaciro ndetse no gukura,

144
00:07:41,844 --> 00:07:44,769
ariko tuzanafata
zimwe muri izi ngingo

145
00:07:44,770 --> 00:07:46,838
zo guhindura umushinga wawe
gato.

146
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,957
Gukura, gukuza imishinga, n'ibindi..

147
00:07:48,958 --> 00:07:51,897
Nibyo dutegereje 
kandi mugumane natwe.

148
00:07:51,898 --> 00:07:53,790
Kugeza mu cyumweru gitaha, tube tukiri kumwe.
